The paper deals with indexing and querying large-scale graph data, which is a common problem in data structures (cs.DS) and databases (cs.DB). The focus on reachability queries also suggests information retrieval (cs.IR) as a possible category. The use of interval labeling and scalability of the method may also relate to systems and networking (cs.SI) and control theory (cs.SY).
